## Summary: Complete Level Lifecycle

```
Boot → PlatformRoot (GameBootstrapper)
         ↓
    HomeScene (loaded additively via SceneLoader)
         ↓
    [MainMenu (standalone) or HomeScene hub → PortalBuilding]
         ↓
    StartGameButton.OnStartGameClicked()
      ├─ Standalone: SceneManager.LoadScene("GameScene")
      └─ Module mode: ModuleManager.ActivateModule("towerdefense") → SceneLoader.LoadSceneAdditive("TDGameScene")
         ↓
    GameManager.Start() → LoadLevel(0)
         ↓
    LevelBuilder.BuildLevel(currentLevelData) → builds tilemaps from ASCII map
         ↓
    Player plays → waves → victory or game over
         ↓
    VictoryPanel:
      ├─ Restart:  GameManager.RestartGame() → reloads scene
      ├─ NextLevel: GameManager.LoadLevel(nextIndex) → same scene, new LevelData
      └─ MainMenu: SceneManager.LoadScene("HomeScene" | "MainMenu")
         ↓
    SaveSystem.SaveLevelProgress() → unlocks next level in save data
```

